0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"确实是。\n燐子同学，你知道这家店？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"不……只是在官网的评论里，\n有这样一条留言……\n『到了大阪后，请一定要去品尝』……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf01_openeye","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event204-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"那句话我好像也看到了！\n其他地方的粉丝们也留了『来我们这儿就尝尝这个吧！』，\n『买土特产我推荐这个！』之类的留言呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event204-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"我觉得这说明了Roselia有多么受人欢迎哦。\n宣布要办全国巡演后，\n粉丝们真的都非常热情！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"特别是最近几天，因为巡演第